<div class="header">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <%= image_tag "logo_v3.png", class: 'img-responsive' %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <div class="primarySell">
          <h1>Convert your tweet into a targeted Ad</h1>
          <h4>
            Share your tweet only with people interested in your product
          </h4>
          <a href="#footer">Start free trail now</a>


          <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
              <%= image_tag "header_screenshot_social_media.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>


<div class="container">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <div class="sellStatement">
        <h1>
          Stop burning money on ineffective Twitter ads
        </h1>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<div class="benefits">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
        <div class="row feature">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h5>Find customers</h5>
            <h3>Interested people</h3>
            <p>
              Do you know how to quickly find people on Twitter talking about <span style="font-weight: bold">products like yours?</span> We take the complexity out of finding those people so that you can focus on talking to them and building up fans and selling more.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <%= image_tag "find_tweet.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </div>




        <div class="row feature">
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <h5>Targeted Ads</h5>
            <h3>Intent based Ads</h3>
            <p>
              The advertisements you are putting out today are keyword based. There is no way to differentiate between salsa the dance and salsa the food item.
            </p>
            <p>
              We have changed all that so that your messages are only shown to people that have the right kind of interest. Our application reads and understands every tweet to match you up with people that are talking about things related to your product. This is just like what a sales person would do to find tweets that relate to your business.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6">
            <%= image_tag "algo.png", class: "img-responsive" %>
          </div>
        </div>






      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</div>



<div id="footer">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">


        <h3 class="text-center">Sign up today to be notified when we launch the app!</h3>

        <div class="row">
          <div class="col-md-8 col-md-offset-2">
            <!-- Begin MailChimp Signup Form -->

            <div id="mc_embed_signup">
              <form action="//urbanzeak.us8.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=589eee1b7d24dfc49b60166d9&amp;id=b7e1497b5c" method="post" id="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" name="mc-embedded-subscribe-form" class="validate" target="_blank" novalidate>
                <div id="mc_embed_signup_scroll">

                  <input type="email" value="" name="EMAIL" class="email" id="mce-EMAIL" placeholder="Email address" required style="width: 100%;padding: 10px 5px;">
                  <input type="text" value="" name="MMERGE1" class="" id="mce-MMERGE1" placeholder="Industry you cater to" required style="width: 100%; padding: 10px 10px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-top: 10px;">
                  <!-- real people should not fill this in and expect good things - do not remove this or risk form bot signups-->
